review_text:
update: i got an email from their lawyer stating that i had never visited the place and that my review would be deleted unless i provide proof. it’s quite ridiculous, i would recommend improving your service instead of bullying your dissatisfied customers.
//
the lemonade was very good, the avocado toast was okay at best, but i didn’t feel welcomed by the staff - waited so long to be seated and then served (had to get the menu on my own and then order at the counter), they also got me a different drink than i ordered. i wished for a better experience but unfortunately my expectations were not met:(
